<TITLE> Lobi's wife arrested </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, June 29 (bdnews24.com)  Police arrested the wife of former BNP lawmaker Ali Asghar Lobi Thursday noon. Gulshan police chief Rawshan Ali said Khushnud Asghar arrested at Labaid Cardiac Hospital and being treated there under police guard. Lobi is in jail now. More than one nurse at the hospital told bdnews24.com that she was admitted to the hospital on June 17 for heart disease and high blood pressure. On March 21, the Anticorruption Commission filed a case against Lobi and his wife for submitting their wealth statements that do not match their real wealth. bdnews
